<paragraph id="7815BCAE92B768B44AA58BFFB8AD179F" pageId="1" pageNumber="102">
Based on 
<taxonomicName id="A8F4B09B9210C773FA6421E64082ED68" authorityName="Feuillet" authorityYear="2016" baseAuthorityName="Feuillet" baseAuthorityYear="2016" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Boraginaceae" genus="Tournefortia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Tournefortia humilis" order="Boraginales" pageId="1" pageNumber="102" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="humilis">
<emphasis id="DF0056193BB9D6F7D0D1B0F5D422817B" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="102">Tournefortia humilis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
L.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="89263D205129A6544E6E740D1045E81C" pageId="1" pageNumber="102" type="notes">
<paragraph id="9596400D1BD404F58351894E5C11C59D" pageId="1" pageNumber="102">Notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="E28706A8B3CF04891B3DF8972FBEDC52" pageId="1" pageNumber="102">
When 
<bibRefCitation id="3B707AD33FBCA5555E0763E2B956D9A5" author="Melo, JIM" journalOrPublisher="Kew Bulletin" pageId="11" pageNumber="112" pagination="285 - 289" publicationUrl="10.1007/s12225-009-9109-3" refId="B44" refString="Melo, JIM, Semir, J, 2009. Two new species and new combinations in Euploca (Heliotropiaceae). Kew Bulletin 64 (2): 285 - 289, DOI: 10.1007/s12225-009-9109-3" title="Two new species and new combinations in Euploca (Heliotropiaceae)." url="10.1007/s12225-009-9109-3" volume="64" year="2009">Melo and Semir (2009</bibRefCitation>
: 289) transferred 
<taxonomicName id="E790CD8771021769A955571DC4A7A99B" authorityName="Feuillet" authorityYear="2016" baseAuthorityName="Feuillet" baseAuthorityYear="2016" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Heliotropiaceae" genus="Heliotropium" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Heliotropium ternatum" order="Boraginales" pageId="1" pageNumber="102" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="ternatum">
<emphasis id="1DBE01B92CAC66482A20B8B4B3470BB7" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="102">Heliotropium ternatum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<bibRefCitation id="E8D9CCEB9DCA68C69F8762FDF4507A40" author="Vahl, MH" journalOrPublisher="Moeller, Copenhagen" pageId="12" pageNumber="113" pagination="1 - 106" publicationUrl="http://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/item/118639page/313/mode/1up" refId="B68" refString="Vahl, MH, 1794. Symbolae botanicae. Moeller, Copenhagen: 1 - 106, http://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/item/118639page/313/mode/1up" title="Symbolae botanicae" url="http://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/item/118639page/313/mode/1up" year="1794">Vahl (1794</bibRefCitation>
, 3: 21) to 
<taxonomicName id="EABA54918399FF8E1BB1EECB15C108C7" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Heliotropiaceae" genus="Euploca" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Euploca" order="Boraginales" pageId="1" pageNumber="102" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="D5904B55FFA27AFC1A8A07E1D5E053F0" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="102">Euploca</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, they did not cite synonyms and they overlooked the case of 
<taxonomicName id="1F73AF32D7FCE4B30AF33F8C67A5F748" authorityName="Feuillet" authorityYear="2016" baseAuthorityName="Feuillet" baseAuthorityYear="2016" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Boraginaceae" genus="Tournefortia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Tournefortia humilis" order="Boraginales" pageId="1" pageNumber="102" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="humilis">
<emphasis id="DB18A61FE1D19E4635BE232C5359D90D" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="102">Tournefortia humilis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
L. There had been a doubt about the exact identity of the Linnean species (
<bibRefCitation id="A495582D2517EAE2576B6160AC913191" author="Johnston, IM" journalOrPublisher="Journal of the Arnold Arboretum" pageId="11" pageNumber="112" pagination="111 - 188" publicationUrl="http://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/part/18048/summary" refId="B29" refString="Johnston, IM, 1949. Studies in the Boraginaceae XVIII. Boraginaceae of the southern West Indies. Journal of the Arnold Arboretum 30: 111 - 188, http://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/part/18048/summary" title="Studies in the Boraginaceae XVIII. Boraginaceae of the southern West Indies." url="http://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/part/18048/summary" volume="30" year="1949">Johnston 1949</bibRefCitation>
: 136; 
<bibRefCitation id="D577AE91541B60C2FCCCC0582BD5A862" author="Foerther, H" journalOrPublisher="Sendtnera" pageId="10" pageNumber="111" pagination="35 - 241" publicationUrl="http://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/item/52056page/1/mode/2up" refId="B15" refString="Foerther, H, 1998. Die infragenerische Gliederung der Gattung Heliotropium L. und ihre Stellung innerhalb der subfam. Heliotropioidea (Schrad.) Arn. (Boraginaceae). Sendtnera 5: 35 - 241, http://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/item/52056page/1/mode/2up" title="Die infragenerische Gliederung der Gattung Heliotropium L. und ihre Stellung innerhalb der subfam. Heliotropioidea (Schrad.) Arn. (Boraginaceae)." url="http://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/item/52056page/1/mode/2up" volume="5" year="1998">
<normalizedToken id="88340416B2D7CB7AB6F52709A8DA93EB" originalValue="Förther">Foerther</normalizedToken>
1998
</bibRefCitation>
: 190), but the typification of 
<taxonomicName id="4DE39D6E205B896F5B4B97FD8A8B8BAA" authorityName="Feuillet" authorityYear="2016" baseAuthorityName="Feuillet" baseAuthorityYear="2016" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Boraginaceae" genus="Tournefortia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Tournefortia humilis" order="Boraginales" pageId="1" pageNumber="102" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="humilis">
<emphasis id="4963EA078181747EBB36D804F88AF688" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="102">Tournefortia humilis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
L. by Miller (in 
<bibRefCitation id="D39892AB0FC4228BF4D95C75920AFA78" author="Cafferty, S" journalOrPublisher="Taxon" pageId="10" pageNumber="111" pagination="799 - 805" publicationUrl="10.2307/4135454" refId="B3" refString="Cafferty, S, Jarvis, CE, 2004. Typification of Linnaean plant names in Boraginaceae. Taxon 53 (3): 799 - 805, DOI: 10.2307/4135454" title="Typification of Linnaean plant names in Boraginaceae." url="10.2307/4135454" volume="53" year="2004">Cafferty and Jarvis 2004</bibRefCitation>
: 804) placed clearly that species in the synonymy of 
<taxonomicName id="03D73C9E0C79AD9580FD6084EE877988" authorityName="Feuillet" authorityYear="2016" baseAuthorityName="Feuillet" baseAuthorityYear="2016" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Heliotropiaceae" genus="Heliotropium" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Heliotropium ternatum" order="Boraginales" pageId="1" pageNumber="102" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="ternatum">
<emphasis id="CCB02BFB97207C2825FB93991E7DE910" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="102">Heliotropium ternatum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Vahl (non 
<taxonomicName id="F7C919303DC2D1F0569767E7E911A905" authorityName="Feuillet" authorityYear="2016" baseAuthorityName="Feuillet" baseAuthorityYear="2016" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Heliotropiaceae" genus="Heliotropium" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Heliotropium humile" order="Boraginales" pageId="1" pageNumber="102" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="humile">
<emphasis id="C3A60B258BAB73187B705EC6E5E0C948" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="102">Heliotropium humile</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Lam.). The epithet of 
<taxonomicName id="DC3588128A28A7221A399C881722AEC4" authorityName="Feuillet" authorityYear="2016" baseAuthorityName="Feuillet" baseAuthorityYear="2016" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Boraginaceae" genus="Tournefortia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Tournefortia humilis" order="Boraginales" pageId="1" pageNumber="102" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="humilis">
<emphasis id="AE74A6DB083B6ECF71A7C5EDF4B16219" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="102">Tournefortia humilis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
could not be transferred to 
<taxonomicName id="75D797D6570DAEEE845C43B8EFA6D6B6" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Heliotropiaceae" genus="Heliotropium" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Heliotropium" order="Boraginales" pageId="1" pageNumber="102" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="6DEB66F36DF737826CA865BF4F9DAE28" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="102">Heliotropium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, but there is no previous 
<taxonomicName id="04B2F2F1CDF50EE2B459219F931E226A" authorityName="Feuillet" authorityYear="2016" baseAuthorityName="Feuillet" baseAuthorityYear="2016" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Heliotropiaceae" genus="Euploca" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Euploca humilis" order="Boraginales" pageId="1" pageNumber="102" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="humilis">
<emphasis id="D4D3564D5567C26BF4A5E2628728F529" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="102">Euploca humilis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and the priority rule dictates the adoption of the new combination (
<bibRefCitation id="6463F55890EB964C6B3845DC126C9975" author="McNeill, J" journalOrPublisher="Koeltz, Koenigstein" pageId="11" pageNumber="112" publicationUrl="http://www.iapt-taxon.org/nomen/main.php" refId="B42" refString="McNeill, J, Barrie, FR, Buck, WR, Demoulin, V, Greuter, W, Hawksworth, DL, Herendeen, PS, Knapp, S, Marhold, K, Prado, J, Prud'Homme van Reine, WF, Smith, GF, Wiersema, JH, Turland, NJ, 2012. Regnum Vegetabile 154. In: International Code of Nomenclature for Algae, Fungi, and Plants (Melbourne Code). Koeltz, Koenigstein, http://www.iapt-taxon.org/nomen/main.php" title="Regnum Vegetabile 154" url="http://www.iapt-taxon.org/nomen/main.php" volumeTitle="International Code of Nomenclature for Algae, Fungi, and Plants (Melbourne Code)." year="2012">McNeill et al. 2012</bibRefCitation>
: Art. 11.4).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="94F522D3EB3956FB5B4F170CD3A0A8A4" pageId="1" pageNumber="102">
Because the name 
<taxonomicName id="005BB513F6DC5F6D8960A1DEEA429240" authorityName="Feuillet" authorityYear="2016" baseAuthorityName="Feuillet" baseAuthorityYear="2016" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Boraginaceae" genus="Tournefortia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Tournefortia humilis" order="Boraginales" pageId="1" pageNumber="102" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="humilis">
<emphasis id="4C7011B64A079DB979FFCFE1918B2C1D" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="102">Tournefortia humilis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
L. or/and 
<taxonomicName id="EC8FE29392B61BE8541EF1587A2DAA51" authorityName="Feuillet" authorityYear="2016" baseAuthorityName="Feuillet" baseAuthorityYear="2016" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Heliotropiaceae" genus="Heliotropium" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Heliotropium humile" order="Boraginales" pageId="1" pageNumber="102" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="humile">
<emphasis id="2A75237246CF95DC4099514E3EC5F4C1" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="102">Heliotropium humile</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(L.) R.Br. ex Roem. &amp; Schult. (1819, 4: 37; non Lam., 1791: 393) have been used in synonymy (
<bibRefCitation id="A6B20C69CD027215D50F42896DE6E46D" author="Johnston, IM" journalOrPublisher="Contributions from the Gray Herbarium" pageId="11" pageNumber="112" pagination="3 - 73" publicationUrl="http://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/item/122400page/1/mode/1up" refId="B26" refString="Johnston, IM, 1928. Studies in the Boraginaceae VII. The South American Species of Heliotropium. Contributions from the Gray Herbarium 81: 3 - 73, http://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/item/122400page/1/mode/1up" title="Studies in the Boraginaceae VII. The South American Species of Heliotropium." url="http://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/item/122400page/1/mode/1up" volume="81" year="1928">Johnston 1928</bibRefCitation>
: 69; 
<bibRefCitation id="CA845EC27174B6EFF07949341D97C1A7" author="Johnston, IM" journalOrPublisher="Journal of the Arnold Arboretum" pageId="11" pageNumber="112" pagination="111 - 188" publicationUrl="http://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/part/18048/summary" refId="B29" refString="Johnston, IM, 1949. Studies in the Boraginaceae XVIII. Boraginaceae of the southern West Indies. Journal of the Arnold Arboretum 30: 111 - 188, http://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/part/18048/summary" title="Studies in the Boraginaceae XVIII. Boraginaceae of the southern West Indies." url="http://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/part/18048/summary" volume="30" year="1949">1949</bibRefCitation>
: 135; and especially the recent revision of 
<taxonomicName id="38F07D6E63EB091EF10C830DF53DB8DC" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Heliotropiaceae" genus="Heliotropium" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Heliotropium" order="Boraginales" pageId="1" pageNumber="102" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="9E1EEDF49621B4593101C72A337C887D" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="102">Heliotropium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<bibRefCitation id="F609FC2C879D35EA148E92E9A3B05289" author="Foerther, H" journalOrPublisher="Sendtnera" pageId="10" pageNumber="111" pagination="35 - 241" publicationUrl="http://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/item/52056page/1/mode/2up" refId="B15" refString="Foerther, H, 1998. Die infragenerische Gliederung der Gattung Heliotropium L. und ihre Stellung innerhalb der subfam. Heliotropioidea (Schrad.) Arn. (Boraginaceae). Sendtnera 5: 35 - 241, http://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/item/52056page/1/mode/2up" title="Die infragenerische Gliederung der Gattung Heliotropium L. und ihre Stellung innerhalb der subfam. Heliotropioidea (Schrad.) Arn. (Boraginaceae)." url="http://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/item/52056page/1/mode/2up" volume="5" year="1998">
